This paper belongs to the field of natural language processing and machine translation, which is covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. The most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which specifically deals with the study of computational models for natural language processing. The paper also involves the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for machine translation and information retrieval (cs.IR) for evaluating the quality of translations. Additionally, the paper discusses the need for deep factual knowledge, which is related to the field of machine learning (cs.LG) and the use of domain-specific knowledge (cs.CY).
